WEBVTT

00:00:28.960 --> 00:00:30.856
They reveal something about creativity,

00:00:30.880 --> 00:00:32.095
our ingenuity --

00:00:32.119 --> 00:00:34.440
they even hint at our identity.

00:00:37.240 --> 00:00:39.496
And when bridges fail,

00:00:39.520 --> 00:00:41.416
or are destroyed in conflict,

00:00:41.440 --> 00:00:43.216
communities struggle,

00:00:43.240 --> 00:00:45.240
development stagnates, people suffer.

00:00:47.280 --> 00:00:49.096
Even today,

00:00:49.120 --> 00:00:53.016
there are over one billion people
living in poor, rural communities

00:00:53.040 --> 00:00:54.256
around the world

00:00:54.280 --> 00:00:56.216
that do not have safe, year-round access

00:00:56.240 --> 00:00:58.696
to the things that you
and I take for granted:

00:00:58.720 --> 00:01:01.280
education, medical care,
access to markets ...